aking it one of the best washer dryers in terms of energy use.","This LG has an extensive number of washing cycles, a full range of drying cycles and a bright digital display."]},"id":"c405d039-2213-40b4-b4f3-ecfb168e42f3","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Functionality"},"id":"8cf8b820-0253-401e-a170-bdd61a1262e7","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/QwkXKKwT6uGPQMwUpZEmwZ.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/67035-lg-wm3477hw2.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/QwkXKKwT6uGPQMwUpZEmwZ.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"QwkXKKwT6uGPQMwUpZEmwZ","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/QwkXKKwT6uGPQMwUpZEmwZ.jpg","alt":""},"id":"c066ebcc-795e-42b6-9a24-c5cf8c70fbe5","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["This combination washer dryer had the second largest drum we tested but is still compact enough to store away in a closet. The LG’s length and width is about 2 square feet, and it’s a little less than three feet tall. The front door to the drum is large with a transparent window, making it easy to load and see the machine working.","The LG comes with nine different washer settings. That’s not the highest number of the machines we reviewed, but it’s more than sufficient. One concern you might have is that the unit doesn’t allow you to change the soil level. If you have heavier, soiled clothes, you can choose the proper preprogrammed cycle, but you don’t have the same level of control that the best washer dryer combo we reviewed offers."]},"id":"6fe157ce-50f3-4b61-a080-aa2194b653a6","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Price"},"id":"d6454992-bd5b-4095-8089-3238ee8e8a61","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/yxKGErUj7tTx23BPfDXbqG.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/67035-lg-wm3477hw4.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/yxKGErUj7tTx23BPfDXbqG.jpg","credit":"","al