oad it. Still, the 6Motion technology helps to keep the load even in the drum. When the load is complete, you hear a loud beep, which can’t be silenced."]},"id":"798efd6e-000c-4f90-bd1e-08ba65e5711a","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Warranty &amp; Support"},"id":"9135742b-7d41-4133-aba8-793b67f3ea1c","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The LG website is full of support options. A full PDF of the manual is available on the main page, and the product support page is easy to find on the right hand side. Customer service is available at all times, and live chat is open on the weekdays.","One major advantage this washer dryer combo offers is an extensive warranty. The motor is covered for 10 years, and the wash drum is covered for the life of the machine. The majority of these appliances are only covered for one year."]},"id":"39457f9c-d27a-4e77-86c6-b108a07f56f6","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"a4606c96-5152-4f24-ab29-99d7e3720cc1","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The LG WM3477HW is nearly perfect but lacks a few cycles and doesn’t have extra features to limit the noise of a busy machine. The 6Motion technology made it one of our best reviewed machines at pure cleaning, and its large door makes for an easy loading experience. The warranty is by far one of the best available. This is a solid machine for your small apartment or condo and a perfect fit if you’re looking for a compact washer dryer with a small footprint."]},"id":"9dfd2451-a890-4316-8713-c70ea747b83e","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_67063","url":"/lg-wm3477hw-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"angie-parkinson","url":"/author/angie-parkinson","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Angie Parkinson","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"4Pu3Dbh8P3CR8CNSJRVPZP","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2015-09-23T15:49:41Z","datePublished":"2015-09-23T15:49:41Z","name":"LG All-in-